<!--#include file="common/includes/header.asp"--><h2>Prime Services</h2>
                         <p>RMB Global Markets Prime Services division  provides execution, financing, asset servicing, custody and clearing facilities  to our largely institutional client base. We facilitate product and trading  needs in the equities, fixed income, currencies and commodities markets. Our  diverse and experienced team is supported by RMB's solid operational, IT,  market and credit risk infrastructure. Our innovative thinking and robust world-class systems enable us to  partner with you to create long-term, reliable and sustainable solutions to meet  your business requirements. Process control, accuracy and efficiency are  core to our service offering.<br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
                         <h3>                       Prime Broking</h3>
                         <p>                           RMB is a leading multi-asset class service  provider to the South African hedge fund industry. <br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
                         <h3>Securities Lending</h3>
                         <p>                         We offer innovative solutions to meet your  securities borrowing or lending requirements through a well-balanced programme  designed to maximize returns and minimize risk.<br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
                         <h3>                         Futures Clearing</h3>
                         <p>                         We provide clearing services for all JSE  listed futures and options across the following products: equities, commodities,  currencies, interest rates and international equity futures (IDX). <br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
                         <h3>                         Stockbroking operations</h3>
                         <p>We provide back-office support, settlement  and custody for JSE-registered institutional stockbrokers, settling through our  RMB Custody division.<br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
                         <h3>                         Reporting  Solutions</h3>
                         <p>                         We provide multi-asset class and multi-manager  reporting on an individual and consolidated basis, including mandate  compliance, regulatory and risk reporting.<br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
                         <h3>                         RMB Custody and Trustee Services</h3>
                         <p>                           We provide securities settlement and  banking facilities to local and foreign financial institutions. <br />
                           <br />
                         </p>
